snippet.title: Terraria: Journeys End trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
Terraria's next big update adds (and changes) a lot, including adding 120 percent more items, golfing, and an ultra-hardcore difficulty mode.

Find out more details here: https://www.pcgamer.com/terraria-unveils-the-huge-journeys-end-update/
